sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title FSD-UC-010 â€” Respaldo automatico diario

    participant SCH as Scheduler_0200_BOT
    participant JOB as Job_Backup
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant VOL as Volumen_Evidencias
    participant STORE as Almacen_Secundario
    participant LOG as LOG_AUDITORIA
    participant JD as Jefatura_DUEA

    SCH->>JOB: trigger diario 02:00
    JOB->>DB: pg_dump
    JOB->>VOL: snapshot blobs de Evidence
    alt BKP-001 fallo dump
        JOB->>LOG: BACKUP_FAILED
        JOB->>JD: alerta 15 min
    else OK
        JOB->>JOB: SHA-256 paquete
        JOB->>STORE: PUT sin sobrescribir valido
        JOB->>LOG: BACKUP_COMPLETED hash
    end
